y}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/SiegfriedEhret/received_events", "type": "User", "user_view_type": "public", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 1, "created_at": "2020-11-24T03:07:38Z", "updated_at": "2020-11-24T05:57:00Z", "closed_at": "2020-11-24T05:57:00Z", "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR", "active_lock_reason": null, "draft": false, "pull_request": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Canop/broot/pulls/307", "html_url": "https://github.com/Canop/broot/pull/307", "diff_url": "https://github.com/Canop/broot/pull/307.diff", "patch_url": "https://github.com/Canop/broot/pull/307.patch", "merged_at": "2020-11-24T05:57:00Z"}, "body": "Hello!\r\nIn https://dystroy.org/broot/icons/ the link to the ttf file ends in a 404 error.\r\nHere is a fix using the master branch version, I hope that's ok.\r\nPeace!", "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Canop/broot/issues/307/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Canop/broot/issues/307/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null, "score": 1.0}, {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Canop/broot/issues/299", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Canop/broot", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Canop/broot/issues/299/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Canop/broot/issues/299/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Canop/broot/issues/299/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/Canop/broot/pull/299", "id": 738477369, "node_id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0NTE3MzE0MDAz", "number": 299, "title": "Add support for icons", "user": {"login": "asdf8dfafjk", "id": 67588957, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjY3NTg4OTU3", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/67588957?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/asdf8dfafjk", "html_url": "https://github.com/asdf8dfafjk", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/asdf8dfafjk/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/asdf8dfafjk/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/asdf8dfafjk/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/asdf8dfafjk/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/asdf8dfafjk/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/asdf8dfafjk/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/asdf8dfafjk/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/asdf8dfafjk/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/asdf8dfafjk/received_events", "type": "User", "user_view_type": "public", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 7, "created_at": "2020-11-08T14:29:23Z", "updated_at": "2022-09-11T02:33:56Z", "closed_at": "2020-11-19T17:15:38Z", "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR", "active_lock_reason": null, "draft": false, "pull_request": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Canop/broot/pulls/299", "html_url": "https://github.com/Canop/broot/pull/299", "diff_url": "https://github.com/Canop/broot/pull/299.diff", "patch_url": "https://github.com/Canop/broot/pull/299.patch", "merged_at": "2020-11-19T17:15:37Z"}, "body": "Support for icons.\r\n\r\nIncluded:\r\n\r\n1) Code changes\r\n2) Resources\r\n3) Doc change\r\n\r\nNot included: \r\n\r\nAutomated testing\r\n\r\nManual testing steps:\r\n\r\n1) Install `resources/icons/vscode/vscode.ttf` . For linux, copy  to ~/.local/share/fonts. You shouldn't need to run `fc-cache` but run it anyway. \r\n\r\n2) In a new terminal, type `echo -e \"file_type_rust looks like \\U001002D2\"` in bash/zsh or\r\n\r\n```\r\n# Powershell escape char is backtick\r\necho \"Rust is `u{1002D2}\"\r\n```  \r\n\r\nin PowerShell. If you see a gears icon, good. Your setup is complete. Otherwise setup needs to be changed.\r\n\r\n3) In broot config, add `icon_theme=\"vscode\"` \r\n\r\n4) Launch broot in a directory with some rust files.\r\n\r\nI haven't spent much time mapping file extensions to file types, it was getting tiring :-). \r\n\r\n[image](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Canop/broot/8b43d85d07d5f86bbaa896f74baa3f43fcb4c460/website/docs/img/icons.png)  \r\n![icons](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/67588957/98468006-8adbc300-21fe-11eb-9857-82bfdd9ab8b2.png)\r\n\r\n\r\nThe icon set is one of the more popular vscode icon sets- https://github.com/vscode-icons/vscode-icons/ \r\nThat said, I couldn't figure out how to import colors in fonts.  ", "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Canop/broot/issues/299/reactions", "total_count": 1, "+1": 1, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Canop/broot/issues/299/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null, "score": 1.0}, {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Canop/broot/issues/296", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Canop/broot", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Canop/broot/issues/296/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Canop/broot/issues/296/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Canop/broot/issues/296/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/Canop/broot/pull/296", "id": 731241215, "node_id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0NTExMzg0NzIy", "number": 296, "title": "feat: instant break for circular symlinks", "user": {"login": "drahnr", "id": 667047, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjY2NzA0Nw==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/667047?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/drahnr", "html_url": "https://github.com/drahnr", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/drahnr/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users